 in a happy voice.  Jumping up onto the seat of her chair, she turned and hugged the taller half-elven woman.  &quot;And Choco too!&quot; she said, jumping down to run over and hug Lenore's husband.<br>
<br>
&quot;I'm glad I lingered here after returning my breakfast dishes,&quot; she smiled, &quot;I was just having a cup of tea and wondering how to find you.&quot;<br>
