&quot;Ah, it is so good to find you here, and such a surprise.  I had been thinking of you lately.&quot;  Lenore said brightly.<br>
Magpye looked at Lenore and noticed a happier look about her.  The last time they met, she had poured out her heart to her, and a sadness was in those beautiful violet eyes.<br>
Lenore ordered some tea for her and Choco, and joined Magpye at the table.<br>
&quot;So, tell me, old friend.  What have you been doing for all these years?&quot;  Lenore asked as she sipped her tea. <p>Lenore Bravehard
